' *** SCRN_FIL.LST ***                               2nd GFA-Manual, page 20-29
> PROCEDURE screen_fill(fill%)
  '
  ' *** Fill screen fast with Fill-pattern on address fill%
  ' *** For High resolution only
  ' *** Uses Line-A
  '
  ' *** Standard:  x.max&  y.max&
  '
  ACLIP 1,0,0,x.max,y.max
  ARECT 0,0,x.max,y.max,1,0,fill%,15
  ACLIP 0,0,0,x.max,y.max
RETURN
' *********
'
